SmartDoc is the XML utility to create documents. 

It can convert SmartDoc format document to HTML4.0, HTML3.2, LaTeX2e
and Java Help. This is the development version(beta). If you use the
stable one, install textproc/smartdoc. For more information about
SmartDoc, see below: 

WWW: http://www.asamioffice.com/ja/2010/smartdoc/index.html

